Question: Describe winter season in your hometown (do not disclose the name of your hometown).
Answer:
My hometwon locates in the Northwest of China so in winter season it is quite cold outside. The temperature could be as low as -20 degree, but since it is far from Pacific Ocean the weather is always dry. That is totally different from South of China. The temperature is not very low, but it is wet outside, Which causes people feel colder than when they in my hometown.